9. Query language

This needs a natural language layer and a structured DSL.

Natural language examples
	•	“Where should we place our next node for highest coordination gain?”
	•	“What bottlenecks are suppressing growth?”
	•	“Which bridges would unlock the most flow?”
	•	“What parts of the field are fragile to one-node failure?”
	•	“Find underpriced regions with rising momentum but low collision risk.”

Structured DSL example

query:
  domain: retail_geo
  objective:
    maximize: coordination_score
    secondary:
      - position_score
      - resilience_score
  constraints:
    vertical: coffee
    min_sqft: 1800
    max_rent_psf: 42
    drive_time_to_anchor_max: 8
  filters:
    region: virginia_beach_metro
  output:
    top_k: 20
    include_explanations: true


