12. Field Engine formulas

Keep them interpretable at first.

Position

Position = f(access, demand_exposure, friction_inverse, pressure_fit)

Coordination

Coordination = f(complementarity, sequencing_fit, bridge_gain, conflict_reduction)

Resilience

Resilience = f(redundancy, low_dependency_concentration, adaptability, shock_tolerance)

Momentum

Momentum = f(trend_alignment, growth_vector, adoption_velocity, timing_window)

Sovereignty

Sovereignty = f(optionality, low_lock_in, control_surface, reversibility)

The early system should favor legibility over exotic math.

